The clan was divided into three branches:
*Guardians: Spies and enforcers for the family, led by [[Ramul Serrat]].{{Cite digital book/Venom in Her Veins/Kindle|510}} 
*Traders: Managed the family's shipping trade and gambling dens.{{Cite digital book/Venom in Her Veins/Kindle|510}} 
*Travelers: Traveled to the jungles south of Delzimmer each summer to harvest terazul blossoms.{{Cite digital book/Venom in Her Veins/Kindle|510}} Much of the family's income was derived from the terazul trade.
